Comparison of cycle life with different operating windows for all cell types

In terms of the electrical benchmark, the 18650 type cells, in general, show less total capacity and higher total resistance (Fig. 3) as they consist of less material in total. When referring to the weight of the cells, it appears that 18650 type cells exhibit less resistance and less capacity than 21700 type cells, e.g. the SAM INR18650-35E has 1109 mΩ⋅ g\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
